strings: <voice_0x010012A6><se_high>Rosalind: J-Jessica!? When did you get back!?

<voice_0x010012A7><se_high>Jessica: Just now.
But I've got to leave again straight away.
<voice_0x010012A8><se_high>Jessica: I still haven't dealt with the person responsible for Alistair's death... I'm sorry...
<voice_0x010012AA><se_high>Rosalind: ...That's all right. You do what you have to do.
<voice_0x010012AB><se_high>Rosalind: Just make sure you come back when it's all taken care of.
<voice_0x010012AC><se_high>Rosalind: <Cap><hero>, I have something I should like to give to you.
<voice_0x010012AF><se_high>Rosalind: This is Alistair's<endash> This was my son Alistair's armour. I want you to have it. I'm sure it will be of use to you on your travels.
<voice_0x010012B0><se_high>Rosalind: He wouldn't have wanted it to sit here gathering dust... He would have wanted it to be used.
<voice_0x010012B2><se_high>Rosalind: It's what he would have wanted, Jessica.
